      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i walked into the kitchen today and for a split second i actually thought i heard him moving around in the other room. then it hit me all over again. the house is just... empty. i don't even know why i bother waking up and going through the motions. everything feels so pointless now.",
