      "content": "You're not an intruder, you're a reminder. A reminder of what's been taken from you, of what's been lost. You're a constant reminder that he's gone, that he's not coming back. And as for the world spinning without you, it's not like you're the only one who's been affected. Everyone's been hurt, everyone's been changed. But you're still here, still stuck in this limbo of grief and regret. So, no, it doesn't matter if you stay or go. It's all just a pointless exercise in survival.",
